us-grc1:9:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.50</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n80306.2\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">on land, going by land</tr_>, opp. sea-faring, esp.in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ δ᾽ ἐθέλεις π., πάρα τοι δίφρος τε καὶ ἵπποι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:324\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.324</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐ μὲν γάρ τί σε πεζὸν ὀΐομαι ἐνθάδ᾽ ἱκέσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:173\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.173</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔφθης πεζὸς ἰὼν ἢ ἐγὼ σὺν νηῒ μελαίνῃ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:58\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.58</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.29</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐν νηῒ θοῇ ἢ π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:438\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.438</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n80306.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">in Prose, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ π</foreign>.